reviews.review: It was a fun movie to see in the theater. It stayed true to the original three. JJ Abrams is clearly the better director of the new movies. The story line makes sense and quickly explains how the emperor is back. It gets going form the opening credits and does not slow down. Worth the experience.
Good action.  Solid nostalgia moments. Nice twists.  Much better than last Jedi
Perfect ending to the 9 movie saga!!

I read so many critic reviews that made me dread watching this movie. I'm a lifetime Star Wars fan! But let me tell you....If you love Star Wars, please do not listen to all those negative review. This is the first time I've felt the need to review a movie online...JJ Abrams gave a movie that I felt answered questions in such a smooth way, tied-in all 9 movies, and brought the Skywalker saga to a richly satisfying end. I walked out of the theater with this movie being my favorite of all Star Wars movies. I felt all the characters were done a true justice and given a tearful and applaud-worthy ending...
Things move too quickly but screenplay is great! Fun to wrap up 40 years!!

A perfect Star Wars movie. Humor, action, love, friendship, teamwork. I had goosebumps over and over. Every major plot point I cared about over the years was wrapped up nicely, and I felt the story made perfect sense. What a great movie, can't wait to see it again.

Excellent movie. Great action sequences and cast chemistry with awesome location and new ideas to the Skywalker saga. It definitely makes up for what the Last Jedi was lacking and while there were a few things off overall it is a good movie and fitting close of The Skywalker Saga
Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker is more interested in resolving an entirely new conflict introduced in its opening crawl than being a conclusion to a 9 film series.

I loved this movie. Say what you will but the fan service was amazing. I went into this thinking if this is anything like the trash called The Last Jedi (If you can even call The Last Jedi a Star Wars Movie) I'll never see another Star Wars movie but I was surprised and excited to see what comes next.
Loved this movie.  What a great ending to the incredible Saga
